---
title: Caribbean Beef Rissoles & Avocado Slaw with Charred Corn & Baby Leaves
description: Charred corn is the perfect addition to a colourful slaw, it's juicy and sweet. Keep tastiness going by spicing the beef rissoles in a
Caribbean jerk seasoning. It’s a dish that leaves a pleasant, warm feeling after you're done.

